headline: CHICAGO GOURMET 2025 POWERED BY INVESCO QQQ: PREMIER CULINARY FEST, TICKETS ON SALE JULY 25
summary: Chicago Gourmet, powered by Invesco QQQ, returns with a sports-themed culinary lineup. Tickets go on sale July 25. Invesco QQQ joins as title sponsor, highlighting its dedication to innovation alongside the Illinois Restaurant Association and Southern Glazer's Wine & Spirits.
